        <name>disconnect</name>
        <qualifiedname>conn_mgr_conn_api::disconnect</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>When called, the connectivity implementation should disconnect (disassociate), or stop any in-progress attempts to associate to a network, the bound iface pointed to by if_conn-&gt;iface. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called by <ref refid="group__conn__mgr__connectivity_1gada2b5271b3e5dbcab629e1538b3d8eb4" kindref="member">conn_mgr_if_disconnect</ref>. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
